This update was supposed to drop yesterday, but I wanted to get it right as best as I could. Thank you for letting me open up to you all like this, and sorry it took so long for me to do it.

If you get anything out of this, get this: DON'T LET YOUR INSECURITIES  DICTATE HOW YOU LIVE YOUR LIFE.
